:CHECKLIST
What to Know Before You Start The Way of Kings
[ ] The first 200 pages require patience and a willingness to trust the author
[ ] Taking notes on character names and factions makes the middle section much clearer
[ ] The book rewards rereads because early chapters gain meaning from later reveals
[ ] Committing to the series is a different investment than reading the first book alone
